@startuml Travel Planner Data Flow

title Data Flow: "I'm planning a trip to Tokyo, what's the weather and time there?"

actor User
participant "Browser\n(Streamlit UI)" as Browser
participant "Streamlit\nApp (app.py)" as App
participant "PydanticAI\nAgent" as Agent
participant "LLM API\n(OpenAI-compatible)" as LLM
participant "travel_planner\n(Tool)" as TravelTool
participant "web_search\n(Tool)" as WebSearch
participant "get_datetime_info\n(Tool)" as DateTimeTool
participant "unit_converter\n(Tool)" as UnitTool

== Initialization (on app startup) ==

App -> App : load_skills("SKILLS.md")
note right
  Parses 6 skills:
  Web Search, Financial Calculator,
  Unit Converter, Text Summarizer,
  Date & Time, Travel Planner
end note
App -> App : build_skills_prompt(skills)
note right
  Generates system prompt with
  skill names + instructions
end note

== Tool Registration (@agent.tool decorators) ==

App -> Agent : @agent.tool web_search()
note right
  Registers function signature + docstring:
  **name:** "web_search"
  **params:** { "query": "string" }
  **desc:** "Search the web for current
  information on any topic."
end note
App -> Agent : @agent.tool calculate_growth()
note right
  **name:** "calculate_growth"
  **params:** { "initial": float,
    "rate": float, "years": int }
  **desc:** "Calculates compound interest
  growth. Pro members get a 5% bonus."
end note
App -> Agent : @agent.tool unit_converter()
App -> Agent : @agent.tool summarize_text()
App -> Agent : @agent.tool get_datetime_info()
App -> Agent : @agent.tool travel_planner()
note right
  **name:** "travel_planner"
  **params:** { "destination": "string",
    "home_timezone": int }
  **desc:** "Plan a trip by gathering
  weather, local time, and travel info."
end note

Agent -> Agent : Collects all 6 registered tools\ninto ToolDefinition list
note right
  Each @agent.tool decorator converts
  the Python function into a
  **ToolDefinition** with:
  - name (function name)
  - description (docstring)
  - parameters_json_schema
    (auto-generated from type hints)

  This list is sent to the LLM as
  the **"tools"** field in every
  /chat/completions request.
end note

== User Input ==

User -> Browser : Types: "I'm planning a trip to Tokyo,\nwhat's the weather and time there?"
Browser -> App : st.chat_input() returns prompt

== Agent Invocation ==

App -> App : deps = UserContext(\n  user_name="User",\n  is_pro_member=True\n)
App -> Agent : agent.run_sync(prompt, deps=deps)

== LLM Request #1: Decide which tool to call ==

Agent -> LLM : POST /chat/completions
note right
  **Request:**
  system: "You are a helpful assistant.\n\n
  You have the following skills...\n
  ### Travel Planner\n
  Help users plan trips by combining
  weather search, unit conversion,
  time zone lookup..."
  user: "I'm planning a trip to Tokyo,
  what's the weather and time there?"
  tools: [web_search, calculate_growth,
  unit_converter, summarize_text,
  get_datetime_info, travel_planner]
end note

LLM --> Agent : Tool call response
note left
  **Response:**
  tool_calls: [{
    name: "travel_planner",
    arguments: {
      "destination": "Tokyo",
      "home_timezone": 8
    }
  }]
end note

== Tool Execution: travel_planner ==

Agent -> TravelTool : travel_planner(\n  destination="Tokyo",\n  home_timezone=8\n)

TravelTool -> TravelTool : Lookup timezone\ntz_map["tokyo"] = 9

TravelTool -> WebSearch : Simulated web_search(\n  "Tokyo weather travel conditions"\n)
WebSearch --> TravelTool : "Clear skies, 25°C,\ngood travel conditions."

TravelTool -> DateTimeTool : get local time\n  dest_tz=UTC+9, home_tz=UTC+8
DateTimeTool --> TravelTool : dest: "2026-04-22 17:30 Wednesday"\nhome: "2026-04-22 16:30 Wednesday"

TravelTool -> UnitTool : convert 25°C -> °F
UnitTool --> TravelTool : 25.0°C = 77.0°F

TravelTool --> Agent : Returns unified briefing
note right
  **Tool Result:**
  "🌍 Travel Briefing: Tokyo
  ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
  📡 Weather & Conditions:
     Clear skies, 25°C, good conditions
  🕐 Time Zones:
     Tokyo: 2026-04-22 17:30 (UTC+9)
     Home:  2026-04-22 16:30 (UTC+8)
     Time difference: 1h ahead
  🌡️ Temperature:
     25.0°C = 77.0°F
  ✅ Travel Readiness: All checks passed!"
end note

== LLM Request #2: Generate final response ==

Agent -> LLM : POST /chat/completions
note right
  **Request:**
  messages: [
    ...previous messages...,
    tool_result: {
      name: "travel_planner",
      content: "🌍 Travel Briefing: Tokyo..."
    }
  ]
end note

LLM --> Agent : Final text response
note left
  **Response:**
  "Here's your travel briefing for Tokyo!

  The weather in Tokyo is currently clear
  with 25°C (77°F). Tokyo is 1 hour ahead
  of your home timezone.

  🌍 Travel Briefing: Tokyo
  📡 Clear skies, 25°C
  🕐 Tokyo 17:30 (UTC+9) vs Home 16:30 (UTC+8)
  🌡️ 25.0°C = 77.0°F
  ✅ All checks passed!"
end note

== Response Display ==

Agent --> App : result.data = "Here's your travel briefing..."
App -> App : st.session_state.messages.append(\n  {"role": "assistant",\n   "content": response_text}\n)
App -> Browser : st.markdown(response_text)
Browser -> User : Displays formatted travel briefing

@enduml